main event: A UFO sighting occurred on March 18, 1966 in Kansas City, Kansas, lasting for 45 minutes.
interesting points: The object was reported to be hovering and moving up and down,The sighting involved 3 confirmed witnesses,The observer described the object as having a blinking light on top,No physical evidence or photographs were found,The sighting took place approximately 4 miles southeast of Kansas City Municipal Airport.
witness description: the witnesses are not further identified in the document, but they were described as reliable.
